704062f-b.title: Brooklyn: New York Avenue (East) - Pacific Street
704062f-b.text:
1. East New York Ave. (right), north side, east of Pacific Street to At-
lantic Ave., showing also the Long Island R.R. elevated and the Atlantic Ave.
station. Shown on the left, are buildings on Pacific Street, which at this
point becomes East New York Ave.
August 110, 1936.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
c. East New York Ave., Pacific St. to Atlantic Ave. Neg. A-182
P.L. Sperr  July 24, 1941
